{"type": "article", "id": 18434, "title": "打缆刺绣布包", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-03T07:00:19Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 41, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702115158TwQuhFLlJd5Ptkn3.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这些有古典风格的布包来自以色列设计师 Tamara Efrat，她从欧洲 18 世纪盛行的打缆刺绣中获得灵感，和团队一起开发了 8 种算法公式。通过改变织物的弹性，方向和强度来改变包袋的最终形状。形成的花纹可以更为复杂，但似乎也失去了原有的手工感，是传统技法结合现代技术的一个实验。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115156OKWIED85bZjcakHf.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"771\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115157iorNU0ZtzfwsHMK3.jpg\" width=\"936\" height=\"624\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115157GcpIlHAUF7WsbfPa.jpg\" width=\"936\" height=\"624\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021151581PQVSjEMsJYnuUIb.jpg\" width=\"936\" height=\"708\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75641026\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n"}